{{Quote|These sky mines, they fill the sky with fire and death... I must have more.|[[Raith Sienar/Legends|Raith Sienar]]|<ref name="The New Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology">''[[The New Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology]]''</ref>}}
'''Sky-mines''' were homing weapons used by the [[Judicial Forces/Legends|Judicial Forces]] in [[29 BBY/Legends|29 BBY]], deployed from [[Sky-mine delivery ship]]s. They were shaped like flattened spheres, with quick maneuverability and tracking abilities and high explosive power. They resembled orange blossoms when being deployed.

